<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Registro | BookHive</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .left-panel {
            width: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14532d, #15803d);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 80px;
        }

            .left-panel h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .left-panel p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                max-width: 400px;
                line-height: 1.5;
            }

        .right-panel {
            width: 50%;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 60px 40px;
        }

            .right-panel h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: #1f2937;
            }

            .right-panel p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                color: #6b7280;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

                .right-panel p a {
                    color: #14532d;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    font-weight: bold;
                }

        form {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 350px;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="email"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .btn-register {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .login-link {
            margin-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

            .login-link a {
                color: #14532d;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-weight: bold;
            }

        @@media (max-width: 900px) {
            body

        {
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .left-panel, .right-panel {
            width: 100%;
            height: 50%;
        }

        .left-panel {
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="left-panel">
        <h1>Únete a BookHive 🐝</h1>
        <p>Explora, reserva y disfruta libros desde cualquier lugar. ¡La comunidad lectora te espera!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="right-panel">
        <h2>Crea tu cuenta</h2>
        <p>¿Ya tienes una cuenta? <a href="#">Inicia sesión</a></p>
        <form>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Nombre completo" required>
            <input type="email" placeholder="Correo electrónico" required>
            <input type="text" placeholder="Nombre de usuario" required>
            <input type="password" placeholder="Contraseña" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn-register">Registrarse</button>
            <div class="login-link">
                <a href="#">¿Ya tienes cuenta? Inicia sesión</a>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

